A new version JDemetra+ additional SA algorithms is available.

In addition to the main Graphical user interface (X13-Arima and Tramo-Seats) recent release ( v3.2.2, see previous blog post), a new version (2.1.0) of the [incubator](https://github.com/jdemetra/jdplus-incubator/releases/tag/v2.1.0) has just been published.

The plug-ins contained in the incubator give access to STL+, STS, X12+  and extensions for high-frequency data.

Just download the following files and proceed with installation as described [here](https://jdemetra-new-documentation.netlify.app/t-plug-ins#t-plug-ins-inst)

![](plug-ins.png)
